Good morning!
The LORD is my STRENGTH & my SONG,
and He has become my #SALVATION;
this is my GOD, & I will PRAISE HIM...
Exodus 15:2
#Jesus

Give thanks to the LORD, for He is good;
HIS #LOVE ENDURES #FOREVER.
Psalm 107:1
#Jesus
